{"tid":2345244,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"女團無預警再爆引退！她嘆全球疫情肆虐　離隊後轉行當護士","createTime":"2020-12-29T10:48:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T12:16:52.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6af7eddceb52b4b47d8e1f5e48a41b016c302ecd","tid":2345244,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T10:48:33.000Z","msg":"日本女團NMB48近年隨著主將山本彩、渡邊美優紀等人離隊後，人氣大不如前。現在18歲的「 顏值擔當」偶像成員山本彩加，昨（28號）於大阪NMB劇場舉行個人演唱會時，突然無預警宣布離隊兼引退。她表示今後將轉行從事醫護方面工作，希望未來成為一位護士。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/29/2959484-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F29%2F2959484-PH.jpg&h=626edb7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼山本彩加於個人演唱會上，無預警宣布離隊兼引退。（圖／翻攝自山本彩加IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/29/2959508-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F29%2F2959508-PH.jpg&h=b3eee6c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n山本彩加是從2016年2月9日開始，從NMB48第5期生募集加入NMB團體，更獲力捧成為新世代主將，她表示受到武漢肺炎（COVID-19，2019新型冠狀病毒）疫情的威脅影響，希望能為與病魔搏鬥的人們出一分心力，幫得一個是一個，因而下定決心離隊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/29/2959521-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F29%2F2959521-PH.jpg&h=249846dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲山本彩加表示自己將重事醫護方面工作。（圖／翻攝自山本彩加IG）<br />\n<br />\n今後山本彩加會專心學業，以從事醫護工作之路邁進。目前山本彩加退團日期未定，演唱會結束後，她也在社群平台留言感謝粉絲，並對突然宣布離隊，讓粉絲吃驚表示抱歉，NMB48為根據AKB48的概念而創立的地方性姊妹團，活動區域主要是關西大阪等地。"},{"pid":"bd1f1c805092d9de01fffc243d7a602df7487704","tid":2345244,"uid":43557,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T10:52:28.000Z","msg":"點解唔轉行拍av"},{"pid":"47767ea6fd55a640e23e2d78bec0db1cd60fe45e","tid":2345244,"uid":49004,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T10:57:56.000Z","msg":"山本彩加山本彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"959416a8787600327bec8095202e3f7ff1812c2d","tid":2345244,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T11:03:23.000Z","msg":"好呀.....護士"},{"pid":"1ef526ca77003f13e3d2557108a5abf3c7bfcbad","tid":2345244,"uid":2781,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bd1f1c805092d9de01fffc243d7a602df7487704","tid":2345244,"uid":43557,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T10:52:28.000Z","msg":"點解唔轉行拍av"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T11:54:47.000Z","msg":"都幾難得，好少會轉返做正行<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47359cd4ff6e6a11aa5355dc385a243570b2242a","tid":2345244,"uid":66346,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T12:16:52.000Z","msg":"本身睇好佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}